      <title>对冲基金套利策​​略在拼多多创纪录暴跌中取得回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/hedge-fund-arbitrage-tactic-sees-payoff-in-pdd-s-record-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PDD Holdings Inc. 股价创纪录下跌，为一种抓住股票和公司债券市场之间脱节的流行对冲基金策略带来了收益。]]></description>
